	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Flamen Quirinalis, and when prevented from leaving Rome for his province by Licinius the Pontifex Maximus, was made Pr. Peregrinus (Liv. 37.51.1-6; cf. Cic. Phil. 11.18; Val. Max. 1.1.2; Tac. Ann. 3.58, cf. 71; Serv. ad Aen. 8.552; cf. Liv. Per. 37, and Oxy. Per. line 4)." .
